jq-Timepicker

Is a jQuery timepicker plugin, I developed it because i needed one like this, if you need it feel free to use it.

Examples

create one with am-pm format at 8 am
	$("#timepicker").timepicker({ hours: 8, minutes: 0, seconds: 0, mode: "am" });
			
create one with a 24 hour format at 8 hours
      $("#timepicker").timepicker({ hours: 8, minutes: 0, seconds: 0, format: "24" });


show
Display the time picker
example
    $("#timepicker").timepicker("show");

hide
Hide the time picker
example
    $("#timepicker").timepicker("hide");

update
update the values of the time picker
Example
    $("#timepicker").timepicker("update", { hours: 8, minutes: 0, secconds: 0, mode:"am" });

getValues24
get the values in a 24 hour format
Example:
      $("#format12").timepicker("getValues24");
      
disable
disable the timepicker
Example
      //enable
      $("#datepicker").timepicker("disable", false);
      //disable
      $("#datepicker").timepicker("disable", true);
    
